---
import { SITE } from '../../data/site';
---
<section class="lapor" id="lapor">
  <div class="lapor-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Saluran Aspirasi Rakyat</div>
      <h2>
        Suara Anda, <span class="italic">prioritas kami.</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        Lapor Mas Wapres adalah inisiatif langsung Wakil Presiden untuk mendengar aspirasi rakyat — dari pelosok desa sampai kota besar. Tidak ada birokrasi berlapis. Tidak ada perantara. Hanya Anda dan kerja yang akan kami wujudkan.
      </p>

      <div class="lapor-channels">
        <a href={`https://wa.me/${SITE.whatsappLapor}`} class="lapor-channel" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
          <div class="lapor-channel-icon" aria-hidden="true">💬</div>
          <div>
            <div class="lapor-channel-title">WhatsApp Resmi</div>
            <div class="lapor-channel-desc">+62 811-1704-2204 · 24 jam</div>
          </div>
          <span class="lapor-channel-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href={SITE.laporUrl} class="lapor-channel" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
          <div class="lapor-channel-icon" aria-hidden="true">📋</div>
          <div>
            <div class="lapor-channel-title">Portal Lapor Mas Wapres</div>
            <div class="lapor-channel-desc">lapormaswapres.id · Form digital terverifikasi</div>
          </div>
          <span class="lapor-channel-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href={SITE.sp4nUrl} class="lapor-channel" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
          <div class="lapor-channel-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏛️</div>
          <div>
            <div class="lapor-channel-title">SP4N-LAPOR Nasional</div>
            <div class="lapor-channel-desc">Sistem pengaduan resmi pemerintah</div>
          </div>
          <span class="lapor-channel-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="lapor-stat-card">
        <div class="lapor-stat-num">12,847</div>
        <div class="lapor-stat-label">Aspirasi Diterima · Diperbarui Real-time</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lapor-stat-card">
        <div class="lapor-stat-num">94<span style="font-size:32px">%</span></div>
        <div class="lapor-stat-label">Tingkat Tindak Lanjut</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lapor-stat-card">
        <div class="lapor-stat-num">38<span style="font-size:32px">prov</span></div>
        <div class="lapor-stat-label">Provinsi Terjangkau</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
